{"tid":849393,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"日本兔仔天國：大久野島 🐰🌟🌟🤗","createTime":"2018-10-05T15:59:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T16:54:58.000Z","uid":197098,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2f990a2bee927d7a061f8355116e11998a5cd6","tid":849393,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"大家有沒有去過日本「兔仔天國」大久野島？是兔迷必去的地方！有1000多隻自由自在地兔子活在這裡。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLF7jueXt6oU&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c81e501a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LF7jueXt6oU</a> <br />\n<br />\n但是其實島內的兔仔有很多活得不開心和不長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predatory animals)的威脅，但是牠們很多有生病的、沒有足夠糧食及營養。所以兔迷下次去最好帶牧草, 例如: Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等等，給牠們最基本的糧食，高纖維。不要給高糖份的和零食，例如: 蘿蔔和水果。當兔子有一隻耳向前、一隻耳向後或一隻耳向上、一隻耳垂下，即代表牠有一點不開心或一點憤怒。但當兔子耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。以下video 可看到大久野島兔仔憂愁的時候: <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=2faa60cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a><br />\n<br />\n另一個video 看到兔子憂愁，耳朵越後就越不開心，主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了: <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=1376eefb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）很不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。 <br />\n以下video 也是另一個例子，兔子生病(痙攣): <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a91cb69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">更多關於兔子憂愁的身體語言：</span><a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me%2F&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=65cbabab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.: </span>實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=7512f42b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"7a65694535aaaa26c61b6bad9b512b5044e935e4","tid":849393,"uid":197098,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:22:21.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！:loveliness:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=d17c6a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a> <br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=3e2bPj8DlYzVAIsfueNW0Wi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=8ae5d636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a>"},{"pid":"f635c05b0a7b292a5dd3a83dd334c32a93c7e801","tid":849393,"uid":32692,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:31:00.000Z","msg":"兔兔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e67281106156128f12878088b69fbb689ddc3c","tid":849393,"uid":13138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"去過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"308370ec46281e95a368b97784a269f91ea859dd","tid":849393,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e67281106156128f12878088b69fbb689ddc3c","tid":849393,"uid":13138,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:31:53.000Z","msg":"去過2次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:58:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42770f7a7ec248083853be6873bff754f6f3fac","tid":849393,"uid":89182,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"想去好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f186be5cee0d85980c8e2e4c6f465b8a88dcea8","tid":849393,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c42770f7a7ec248083853be6873bff754f6f3fac","tid":849393,"uid":89182,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T04:59:34.000Z","msg":"想去好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" c